Package: ukbflow
Title: Streamlined Workflow for UK Biobank Data Extraction, Analysis, and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Evan", "Zhou", , "evanzhou.bio@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A streamlined workflow for UK Biobank data extraction, clinical
    analysis, and publication-quality visualization. Covers upstream data
    cleaning and field ID mapping, midstream clinical and association analysis,
    and downstream high-quality plot generation.
